{
  "title": "Dense Smoky Norwegian Beetroot Stew",
  "description": "A romantic Norwegian dish featuring beetroot, this stew is tangy, dense, and smoky, made in a donabe vessel with ayurvedic-tamasic-friendly ingredients. It is perfect for a cold winter night.",
